#X text 280 148 A classic example is to control the cutoff frequency of a filter. By default \, in this example we have a 500 hz cutoff that corresponds to a MIDI pitch of 48 (C3) and a tracking amount of 50%. Hence \, C4 moves the cutoff a tritone higher and C2 a tritone lower., f 35;
