#X text 301 155 You can change the exponential mode to another one based on 'tanh' \, where the exponential factor is actually a saturation factor. This is more suited to generate an S curve that compresses to the extremes. A zero value is linear and negative values also flip horizontally., f 52;
#X text 308 300 Changing the amount also affects the overall range of the curve., f 26;
